static QUOTE_23_45_2: Minute = Minute{title: "Three Men in a Boat", author: "Jerome K. Jerome", start: "We struck the tow-path at length, and that made us happy because prior to this we had not been sure whether we were walking towards the river or away from it, and when you are tired and want to go to bed, uncertainties like that worry you. We passed Shiplake as the clock was striking the ", time: "quarter to twelve", end: " and then George said thoughtfully: “You don’t happen to remember which of the islands it was, do you?”"};
